translated: Jannert, Janne Bertil Gerhard, minister, Riamkvilla, b. 03/11/1913 in Ljungby. Married in 1941 to Ingrid Ida Linnea Håkansson, who attended folk school. Children: Magnus, b. 1945 and Christina, b. 1946. — High school graduate from Katlmi in 1935, Bachelor of Theology from Lund and practical theology training in 1941, ordination the same year. Was a vicar in Forsiheda in 1941, Hultsjö in 1942, vice minister in Ramkvilla from 1942-46, minister there from 1946 onwards. Chairman of the Ramkvilla parish council, church meeting, folk school board and child welfare committee, as well as in the Fröderyd parish church meeting.
